OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FLargely dry through this period, with
OL,7,Fcloud moving inland overnight then
OL,8,Fburning back to the coast by day to
OL,9,Fgive sunny spells. Temperatures around
OL,10,For a little above average.
